name: quadprog
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "quadprog" %}
{% set version = "0.1.11" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8e320f9f7f1466141e317e61736e8108720e6adbae53f9d6960f726efef788d9

build:
  number: 1
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cython                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - cython
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - cython
    - python
    - numpy

test:
  imports:
    - quadprog
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/rmcgibbo/quadprog
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Quadratic Programming Solver

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - nfahlgren
